    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Cheaphaven, your best bet at escaping the outside world by diving into the relaxing world of agriculture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707850/extras/2fa52dcd4724a6286c02922b60efe917.poster.avif?t=1751317284\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707850/extras/2fa52dcd4724a6286c02922b60efe917.webm?t=1751317284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707850/extras/2fa52dcd4724a6286c02922b60efe917.mp4?t=1751317284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take an hour or two off</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend some time fishing, pet a chicken, build a windmill, enjoy the small things in life. Cheaphaven features a brief respite full of farming, building and upgrading, a small town of NPCs for all your chatting and shopping needs, and vaguely humorous descriptions for everyday items. Day/night cycle, market values, sales reputation, a pigeon, all the things that are supposed to be in a farming game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo limitations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo allows you to play for a full in-game week without restrictions. You can keep playing after the demo time ends, but progression won't be possible. Demo save data can be transferred to the full release</p>",
